# decisions/

## What goes here
- Committed choices with known tradeoffs
- Actions taken after weighing alternatives

## What does NOT go here
- Uncommitted ideas still being explored (→ `ideas/`)
- Observations without a choice being made (→ `insights/` or `patterns/`)

## Primary Home Test
File here if a choice was committed with known tradeoffs.

## Naming Rule
`YYYY-MM-DD-decision-name.md`. Example: `2026-04-17-switch-to-postgres.md`

## Required Sections
- Executive Summary
- Bias Check
- Alternatives Considered
- Tradeoffs
- Compiled Truth
- Timeline Evidence
